The death cultist bows his head reverently.
languages.original_text: Культист смерти с почтением склоняет голову.

traits.locale_text: The death cultist bows his head reverently.
The death cultist bows his head reverently without making a sound. His lips are sewn shut with a black thread.

languages.text: Der Todeskultist senkt ehrfürchtig den Kopf.
languages.original_text: The death cultist bows his head reverently.

traits.locale_text: Der Todeskultist senkt ehrfürchtig und lautlos den Kopf. Seine Lippen sind mit einem schwarzen Faden zugenäht.

languages.text: El cultista de la muerte inclina la cabeza con respeto.
languages.original_text: The death cultist bows his head reverently.

traits.locale_text: El cultista de la muerte inclina la cabeza con respeto sin hacer sonido alguno. Sus labios están cosidos con hilo negro.

languages.text: 死のカルト信者は音を立てることなく恭しく頭を下げる。
languages.original_text: The death cultist bows his head reverently.

traits.locale_text: 死のカルト信者は音を立てることなく恭しく頭を下げる。彼の唇は黒い糸で縫い閉じられている。

languages.text: 这位拜死教教徒恭敬地低头致意。
languages.original_text: The death cultist bows his head reverently.

traits.locale_text: 这位拜死教教徒虔诚地低下头，无声无息，他的嘴唇被黑线缝住了。

languages.text: Le cultiste de la mort incline révérencieusement la tête.
languages.original_text: The death cultist bows his head reverently.

traits.locale_text: Le cultiste de la mort incline révérencieusement la tête sans émettre le moindre son. Ses lèvres sont cousues de fil noir.

languages.original_text: The death cultist bows his head reverently.
